You're as cuddly as a cactus,<br />
You're as charming as an eel.<br />
Mr. Grinch.<br />
<br />
You're a bad banana<br />
With a greasy black peel.<br />
<br />
You're a monster, Mr. Grinch.<br />
Your heart's an empty hole.<br />
Your brain is full of spiders,<br />
You've got garlic in your soul.<br />
Mr. Grinch.<br />
<br />
I wouldn't touch you, with a<br />
thirty-nine-and-a-half foot pole.<br />
<br />
You're a vile one, Mr. Grinch.<br />
You have termites in your smile.<br />
You have all the tender sweetness<br />
Of a seasick crocodile.<br />
Mr. Grinch.<br />
